t:
The Empress died during childbirth, giving birth to only one girl.

However, the Emperor wasn't sad.
He had a new Empress.
c:
The bloodline shall remain PURE.


Inspired by the story of Anchorhead.



This story is meant to be open to interpretations. You decide the fate of the new Empress.
